==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Undergraduate
<hw>Un`der*grad"u*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A member of
a university or a college who has not taken his first degree; a student
in any school who has not completed his course. Contrasted with
<contr>graduate student</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Undergraduate</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Undergraduate
<hw>Un`der*grad"u*ate</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to an
undergraduate, or the body of undergraduates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Undergraduateship</ent>⟦br⟧
